<tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" root="false"><frontmatter> <anchor>363</anchor>  <taxon>Definition</taxon> <addr>axt-001W</addr>  <route>axt-001W.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>10</month> <day>26</day></date>  <title>Scott locale of a dcpo</title> </frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>  The Scott locale of a dcpo <tex>D</tex> is the locale given by the frame of opens
